OL,3,CTribunal finds Darlington nurses
OL,4,Csuffered harassment in trans changing
OL,5,Croom case
OL,7,FAn employment tribunal in Newcastle
OL,8,Fhas found that eight Darlington nurses
OL,9,Fwho complained about a trans colleague
OL,10,Fusing single-sex changing rooms at
OL,11,Fwork suffered harassment with the
OL,12,F"effect of violating the dignity of
OL,13,Fthe claimants and creating a hostile,
OL,14,Fintimidating, humiliating and
OL,15,Fdegrading environment for them".
