OL,3,CTribunal finds Darlington nurses
OL,4,Csuffered harassment in trans changing
OL,5,Croom case
OL,7,FThe tribunal rejected the nurses'
OL,8,Fclaims that their transgender
OL,9,Fcolleague, who is a biological male
OL,10,Fand identifies as a woman, using the
OL,11,Fsingle-sex changing room had not
OL,12,Fpersonally engaged in conduct that
OL,13,Famounted to harassment.
OL,15,FIt also rejected the claim that the
OL,16,Ftrust had victimised the claimants.
