OL,3,CTribunal finds Darlington nurses
OL,4,Csuffered harassment in trans changing
OL,5,Croom case
OL,7,FBut the tribunal found that County
OL,8,FDurham and Darlington NHS Foundation
OL,9,FTrust had subjected the nurses to
OL,10,Fharassment by allowing a trans
OL,11,Fcolleague to use a female changing
OL,12,Froom without providing a suitable
OL,13,Falternative.
OL,15,FThe tribunal found the trust did not
OL,16,Ftake their concerns seriously and it
OL,17,Fhad said claimants needed "to be
OL,18,Feducated on trans rights and to
OL,19,Fbroaden their mindsets".
