OL,3,CTribunal finds Darlington nurses
OL,4,Csuffered harassment in trans changing
OL,5,Croom case
OL,7,FIn its judgment, the panel said: "The
OL,8,Fabove conduct had the effect of
OL,9,Fviolating the dignity of the claimants
OL,10,Fand creating a hostile, intimidating,
OL,11,Fhumiliating and degrading environment
OL,12,Ffor them."
OL,14,FDarlington nurse Bethany Hutchison led
OL,15,Fthe claim. After the judgement, she
OL,16,Fsaid: "This is a victory for common
OL,17,Fsense and for every woman who simply
OL,18,Fwants to feel safe at work.
