OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F423A1768833638
OL,3,CTribunal finds Darlington nurses
OL,4,Csuffered harassment in trans changing
OL,5,Croom case
OL,7,F"Women deserve access to single-sex
OL,8,Fspaces without fear or intimidation.
OL,9,FForcing us to undress in front of a
OL,10,Fman was not only degrading but
OL,11,Fdangerous.
OL,13,F"Today's ruling sends a clear message:
OL,14,Fthe NHS cannot ignore women's rights
OL,15,Fin the name of ideology. We stood up
OL,16,Fbecause we knew this was wrong. No
OL,17,Fwoman should be forced to choose
OL,18,Fbetween her job and her safety.
