OL,7,F"This ruling is a turning point, and
OL,8,Fwe will keep fighting until every
OL,9,Fwoman in the NHS is guaranteed the
OL,10,Fdignity and protection she deserves."
OL,12,FThe County Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,13,FFoundation Trust has been contacted
OL,14,Ffor comment.
